rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0001
rows.name:
I never knew salvage training
was that intense...

rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0002
rows.name:
And it's scary, too...
I'm starting to hate the Cloud Sea from the bottom of my heart.

rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0004
rows.name:
We don't have anywhere else to go,
and more than anything, we want to repay the kindness we've been shown.

rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm still no good at it,
but I'm not giving up. I'm going to become a first-rate salvager.
